settings.description: Fun Fact: I'm terrible at making underwater levels, so I just decided to take out the water in the underwater, thus creating an... under level.

So I made the first level of TI2,a SMBX map.
I don't know what's wrong but a gap appears in the bouns room and i cant remove it,then I place a pipe to cover it.Hovever,have fun :)
very old level that I made, just never published it.
Good lord am I bad at puzzles! although... hopefully the ones I made'll be good enough to make you think on where to go to find the exit?
seems this normal ol wooden plains level got flooded by something! best to watch out for the flopping fish, for they can still harm you!
Noyhing too special about this level. Its simple :O
just like how the real e-reader levels have a two part special that's all about one tough as nails challenge.. instead of an airship, you get a huge castle! watch out, The Big Boo awaits you!

who would've thought that such a strange combo would come to be! best to learn how to use them though, and swim swiftly about with such!
PS: I am bad at underwater levels.
